  "texts": [
    "This exclude-include process resulted in 345 article titles which were then extracted based on nine RQs.",
    "The included criteria were further analyzed to find answers based on the nine research questions, as shown in Table 2.",
    "Data extractionAfter retrieving 345 articles, the next step was creating a matrix using a spreadsheet to extract data according to RQ1-RQ9.",
    "The data extraction process was carried out by reading the articles in detail.",
    "Then if data were 912 SYSTEMATIC LITERATURE REVIEW ON NAMED ENTITY RECOGNITION found matched to one of the RQs, they were entered into the matrix."
  ]
}